  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Calculate the torques on rotating systems about a fixed axis to find the angular acceleration</item>
<item>Explain how changes in the moment of inertia of a rotating system affect angular acceleration with a fixed applied torque</item>
</list></md:abstract>
